        "Description": "Good evening, 47. Your target is Cilas Netzke, KGB Officer responsible for multiple plane bombings across the globe. You must also eliminate Edward Evdokimov, a soviet soldier gone rogue who has been hired by an unknown company to spy on the military.\r\rThe two bastards have arrived in an airfield in communist Cuba, and security is tight. Expect many soldiers roaming the area.\r\rThe clock is ticking, 47. Good luck.",
